---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TranscriptMagic">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 2024</p>

      <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          TranscriptMagic ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when
          you use our website and Chrome extensions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>Account Information</h3>
        <p>
          When you sign in with Google, we receive your email address, name, and profile picture
          from Google. This information is used to create and manage your account.
        </p>

        <h3>Usage Data</h3>
        <p>
          We track the number of transcripts generated with your account or device to enforce
          usage limits. We do not store the URLs of videos you transcribe or the video content itself.
        </p>

        <h3>Device Identifiers</h3>
        <p>
          For users who haven't signed in, we generate a random device identifier stored locally
          in your browser to track free trial usage. This identifier is not linked to any
          personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To provide and maintain our service</li>
          <li>To track usage and enforce download limits</li>
          <li>To process payments through our payment provider (Lemon Squeezy)</li>
          <li>To communicate with you about your account or subscription</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          Your account data is stored securely on Cloudflare's infrastructure. We do not store
          video content - transcripts are generated on-demand and delivered directly to your device.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Sign-In</strong> - For authentication</li>
          <li><strong>Lemon Squeezy</strong> - For payment processing</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> - For hosting and infrastructure</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Each of these services has their own privacy policy governing how they handle your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your account information for as long as your account is active. You can
          request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Chrome Extension Permissions</h2>
        <p>Our Chrome extensions require the following permissions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>downloads</strong> - To save transcript files (SRT) to your device</li>
          <li><strong>activeTab</strong> - To detect video pages on supported platforms</li>
          <li><strong>tabs</strong> - To access the current tab URL for transcription</li>
          <li><strong>storage</strong> - To store your preferences and usage data locally</li>
          <li><strong>clipboardWrite</strong> - To copy transcripts to your clipboard</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any
          changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:privacy@transcriptmagic.com">privacy@transcriptmagic.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  section:first-of-type h2 {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  section h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  section ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  section a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
